Definition: deeply affected or marked by mental or physical pain or injury
Example: Could her scarred mind ever be free of fear?; a face scarred by anxiety; the fire left her arm badly scarred
Synonyms: deeply, affected, or, marked, by, mental, physical, pain, injury, Could, her, mind, ever, be, free, of, fear, a, face, anxiety, the, fire, left, arm, badly
Category: adj.all
